      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's looking for a new home! It\u2019s in solid, dependable shape and has been a real joy to drive. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to go. It\u2019s been well-cared for and is just waiting for someone else to enjoy it as much as I have. Come say hi and take it for a spin!",
